'''Domain Anor''' was a [[Domain]] among the [[Intendant caste]] of [[Yuuzhan Vong]] society. By far the most famous member of Domain Anor was the [[Executor (Yuuzhan Vong rank)|Executor]] and later [[Prefect/Legends|Prefect]] [[Nom Anor]], though members of Domain Anor would probably not have considered this a source of pride as he had frequent brushes with disaster during the course of fulfilling his duties. Another known member of this domain was [[Phaa Anor]], a crèche-cousin of Nom.

